{"ID":"20260605150313-3qks7pp","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260605150313-3qks7pp","title":"2021年全国甲卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260605150407"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605150333-ps32g5w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150333-ps32g5w","updated":"20260605150333"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"和南丰先生出山之作"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"①"}]},{"ID":"20260605150333-5y1xaac","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150333-5y1xaac","updated":"20260605150333"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"陈师道"}]},{"ID":"20260605150333-i8076nl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150333-i8076nl","updated":"20260605150333"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"侧径篮舁两眼明​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"②"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​，出山犹带骨毛清​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"③"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150333-737mldu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150333-737mldu","updated":"20260605150333"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"白云笑我还多事，流水随人合有情。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150333-l3klk2t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150333-l3klk2t","updated":"20260605150333"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不及鸟飞浑自在，羡他僧住便平生。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150333-lkivtyq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150333-lkivtyq","updated":"20260605150333"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"未能与世全无意，起为苍生试一鸣。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150333-rr5u5vc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150333-rr5u5vc","updated":"20260605150333"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"【注释】①南丰先生：即曾巩，陈师道敬重仰慕的师长。②侧径：狭窄的路，篮舁：竹轿。③骨毛清：谓超凡脱俗，具有神仙之姿。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150313-5c3xldi","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605150313-5c3xldi","updated":"20260605150345"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260605150345-covauvd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150345-covauvd","updated":"20260605150345"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"14．下列对这首诗的理解和赏析，不正确的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260605150345-5ykhak0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150345-5ykhak0","updated":"20260605150345"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．出山之初的曾巩，展现出来的是一个明净爽利、风骨秀异的高士形象。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150345-zaqr0nc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150345-zaqr0nc","updated":"20260605150345"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．颔联两句使用拟人的修辞手法，表现白云和流水对于曾巩出山的态度。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150345-41guncz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150345-41guncz","updated":"20260605150345"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．住在山中的僧人虽然不能像飞鸟一样自由自在，但其生活也令人羡慕。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150345-716wpax","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150345-716wpax","updated":"20260605150345"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．陈师道在诗中书写了曾巩的人生志趣与处世情怀，笔端饱含敬佩之情。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150345-cuv11ck","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150345-cuv11ck","updated":"20260605150345"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"15．在陈师道看来，曾巩是如何处理“仕”与“隐”的关系的？请简要分析。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150313-mk2g3qz","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605150313-mk2g3qz","updated":"20260605150352"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260605150313-8nb9yl5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150313-8nb9yl5","updated":"20260605150352"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"14．C    15．①在曾巩那里，仕与隐并非截然对立，而是可以兼容于一身的；②曾巩向往离世高蹈、超凡脱俗，但他又不能忘情于天下苍生，原意承担社会责任，有深厚的济世情怀。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150313-4l45o7p","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605150313-4l45o7p","updated":"20260605150407"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260605150407-fkftep7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150407-fkftep7","updated":"20260605150407"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"14．本题考查学生理解赏析诗歌内容及艺术手法的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150407-3ljvtc0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150407-3ljvtc0","updated":"20260605150407"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C.“住在山中的僧人虽然不能像飞鸟一样自由自在，但其生活也令人羡慕”错误，原文“不及鸟飞浑自在，羡他僧住便平生”指的是身在官场，终不如山中飞鸟那般自由自在，隐居山中的僧人，这一生就可以悠然闲适地度过，这种生活真令人羡慕。并不是僧人不像飞鸟一样自由自在，而是作者自己身不如飞鸟自在。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150407-s175q3n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150407-s175q3n","updated":"20260605150407"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选C。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150407-92px686","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150407-92px686","updated":"20260605150407"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"15．本题考查学生分析理解作者思想感情及处世态度的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150407-utfh5hd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150407-utfh5hd","updated":"20260605150407"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"颈联和尾联转到曾巩对“出”与“隐”的看法。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150407-cpxq11n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150407-cpxq11n","updated":"20260605150407"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"颈联说：身在官场，终不如山中飞鸟那般自由自在，隐居山中的僧人，这一生就可以悠然闲适地度过，这种生活真令人羡慕。可以看出，曾巩对隐居生活是充满了向往的。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150407-xt0hppw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150407-xt0hppw","updated":"20260605150407"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尾联“未能与世全无意，起为苍生试一鸣”可见，他与红尘俗世也并非全然了断，为了替天下苍生发声鸣不平，他最终还是放弃了隐居生活，决然出山。在“独善其身”与“兼济天下”之间，他选择了后者，把个人之乐暂且放下，将苍生之忧挂在心头。在这一点上，他与“先天下之忧而忧，后天下之乐而乐”的范仲淹可谓异代同心。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150313-kbn1bt3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150313-kbn1bt3","updated":"20260605142207"}}]}